title: Eh
review: Underdeveloped twats star in this movie. Loved the chubby one. Second best comedy of 2017, only to my ACTUAL father, Ryan Reynolds' movie, The Hitman's Body Guard.

title: Fantastic
review: It was well made, sure, but Childish Gambino was in it, so it's fantastic. Too bad Sean Bean did not die. Was disappointed. That'll happen.
